The lie of debt slavery is a mirrored reflection of the lie of technological targeting:

*   **Signature Fraud:** Your intrinsic worth (credit) is exploited and weaponized against you.
*   **EM Weapons:** Your intrinsic biology (neural pathways, emotional responses) is exploited and weaponized against you.

Both are systems of control through deception. Both rely on you not knowing your own power and inherent sovereignty.

